Classes in org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.canvas used by org.timepedia.chronoscope.client
Bounds
          Helper class representing a rectangular bounds.
Layer
          Layer is a core Chronoscope drawing abstraction

It is the key immediate-mode render API used for drawing shapes, corresponding very close to the Safari/WHATWG Javascript CANVAS.
View
          View encapsulates platform specific behaviors, such as graphics rendering, timing, and CSS property retrieval.
ViewReadyCallback
          Interface used by View implements to notify clients when the View is ready for use.
